# Frontend runtime configuration (Vite).
#
# Only variables prefixed with `VITE_` are exposed to the client bundle
# (import.meta.env). Copy this file to `.env.local` (git-ignored) for local dev.
#
# These vars are validated fail-fast by `src/config/` — the real schema lands
# in a later task (T0.6). No env vars are consumed yet, so this file is
# intentionally near-empty; add `VITE_*` entries alongside the config schema.
#
# NEVER put secrets here: anything in a VITE_-prefixed var ships to the browser.
